ygData.subject: Re: Iksar SK looking for Dungeon
ygData.msgSnippet: IF you can get there, my guildies and I have been having GREAT fun in Runnyeye. There are plenty of higher level mobs in there, plus there s a nice xp bonus.
ygData.messageBody:
IF you can get there, my guildies and I have been
having GREAT fun in Runnyeye. There are plenty of higher
level mobs in there, plus there's a nice xp bonus.
There've been LOTS of changes made to Runnyeye and it's
certainly MUCH more interesting now. BTW... the groups
we've been running have been from 17 to 26... and we
haven't gone all the way in. I'd imagine there's even
MORE stuff the further down you go. <br><br>There's
some pretty phat loot down there too.<br><br>Uaria
Lifebringer, 31 cleric of Bristlebane<br>Rodcet Nife
